+ Introduction

[[div style="background: url(https://i.imgur.com/AE3SJEd.png) center no-repeat; background-size: 70%;"]]

> Hi everyone!, I'm [[*user Machiavellian]], or you'll maybe know me as Fyahgfox at another platform.
> 
> I'm here to show every SCP related art I have ever made so far from late 2020 until now, from 
> __**BnW Crosshatch Traditional Art**__ to __**Full-Color/Monochromatic Digital Art**__
>  
> Oh! besides being an artist, I am also one of the volunteer translators and writers from the unofficial SCP Indonesian Branch (SCP-IDN)
> 
> If you'll want to know more or another art from me, you can find me at :
> 
> [https://linktr.ee/Fyahgfox Linktree]
> 
> Thank you to visit my Artworks Page and I hope you'll enjoy what you see here

[[/div]]
